{
  "stem": "4710.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was-- this was-- this is a point which has overshadowed my happy childhood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I-- as I've grown older, I've learned more and more what is going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by-- by certain-- and as per previous years, there was restrictions on Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we realized it that we are-- we are second-grade citizens and things are not getting better for the Jews as such.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Jewish people were not accepted in the army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to-- they had to cordon in military age into labor battalions under the supervision of the Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the restrictions on businesses, certain licenses have been taken away, restrictions on the-- on the professions.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We felt it already that we are not safe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Possibly, it happened before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was-- as a child, I was not aware of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as-- as I've grown up, my awareness has grown, so I realize it, that-- that it's-- it's Hungary is really not our country.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are here second-class citizens and just hope to pray to God that we will get through the difficult years.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't remember that my parents has discussed it with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in school, with other friends, with older children, you get information.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, by that time, I was reading the newspapers, so I was quite-- quite well aware what is going on in-- in Hungary and also generally in the world.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- always followed-- followed the world news.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was really-- perhaps, even-- even-- even at an early age, I was-- I was-- I was involved in world-- current affairs and what's happening in the world.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember-- I remember when the war started-- in-- when the Germans occupied France, later the Russians attacked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans attacked Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
